{"tid":289510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梅媽反駁生活費沒20萬 9萬不夠用「交租又要食」","createTime":"2017-06-19T05:11:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-20T04:57:43.000Z","uid":3189,"like":73,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d8dfbfc38bfe0be9fd631d1eb5cfe3164c006981","tid":289510,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T05:11:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/sy/ny/api/res/1.2/lwTjlgbkA0FaFVS5p6xbUA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20170619a112840.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fsy%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FlwTjlgbkA0FaFVS5p6xbUA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20170619a112840.jpg&h=7fd7735b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n梅媽一度激動，「得唔夠10萬咋，得9萬幾」。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】已故樂壇天后梅艷芳的母親覃美金（梅媽）去年四月結束破產令，但因爭奪梅艷芳遺產欠下巨額訟費，再遭兩名破產信託人呈請破產。直至今年1月，她共欠訟費連利息共13.4萬多港元。案件今在高院處理，梅媽已繳還欠款，法官正式宣布撤銷本破產案件。<br />\n<br />\n梅媽指澄清外界說她每月有20萬生活費，其實只有9萬，「匯豐（遺產管理人）死都要個個月畀我生活費，剩下的就投資，幾億都洗曬啦！佢好叻嫁，屋租同工人費全部都隊埋畀我，我交完仲有幾多呢？出面的人話我20萬都唔夠洗，根本就無20萬，我得唔夠10萬咋，得9萬幾」，她指9萬都唔夠洗，「工人費啦，仲要交租，又要食啦」。梅媽又指「佢官字兩個口，我得一個口，佢捏住我喉嚨」。<br />\n<br />\n法庭記者：方嘉欣"},{"pid":"cfce9ad70adae4d687bf530c82b982688f636648","tid":289510,"uid":24139,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T05:24:21.000Z","msg":"唔夠使咪去賣紙皮紙箱囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6399bac9f05c8641ead9efd7811f1d5e398407ec","tid":289510,"uid":5702,"like":133,"dislike":1,"score":132,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T05:25:11.000Z","msg":"梅姐生前選擇遺產信託，真係一件做得好岩既事。"},{"pid":"fbee9f4cec7a2a1a9f434ba149e062d14fc7cc3b","tid":289510,"uid":41292,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T05:26:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/sy/ny/api/res/1.2/lwTjlgbkA0FaFVS5p6xbUA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTA